The Darmstadt Artists Colonies leading architect home in Germany\u2028
A mobile application who’s objective was to visually restore the building’s historic appearance and intended design
Used ‘Snapshot’ technology to generate the buildings intended design. Allowed users to view this without the need of holding their phone upright.
